From sketch to real life, discover the #ChooSketch capsule collection, available now. Watch the video to re-live the story and meet our winners #JimmyChoo

100% of profits will go to @womenforwomenuk, a charity helping women survivors of war to rebuild their lives. We are proud to be supporting their vision of working towards a world where every woman's voice, role and contribution are visible and valued #WomenforWomenInternational 
UK Charity Registration Number: 1115109.

node.text:
Presenting Jimmy Choo x Billy Porter: designed by Creative Director @sandrachoiofficial and the award-winning actor @theebillyporter, the capsule champions inclusivity with extended sizing across iconic silhouettes realised in a bold colour palette. Pre order now at JimmyChoo.com #JIMMYCHOOXBILLYPORTER

To mark the collection’s release, Jimmy Choo is supporting @trevorproject, whose mission of ending LGBTQ youth suicide is a cause close to Billy’s heart. Jimmy Choo’s donation will directly support Trevor’s life-saving programs, which include free 24/7 crisis counselling via phone, text and chat for LGBTQ youth. In 2020, Trevor supported more than 150,000 crisis contacts from LGBTQ young people.
